tissueExpression.summary: Most of the normal cells displayed moderate to strong often granular cytoplasmic immunoreactivity. Lymphoid tissues, squamous epithelia, placenta, myocytes, cells in seminiferus ducts and cells of CNS except cerebellum were negative or weakly stained.

subcellularLocation.summary: Localized to the nucleus & mitochondria in both human and mouse cells.
